This is the final step in creating you character.  You are granted four 
bonus rolls to improve the stats of your choice.  A lot can be gained by
placing the bonuses in the right spot, so choose carefully.

Select the stat for the bonus roll by entering the bracketed letter:

   (S)trength            (P)ower        
   (D)exterity           (I)ntelligence 
   (A)gility             (W)isdom       
   (C)onstitution	 C(h)arisma
   (L)uck

